These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-1::.
6 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, hamster, hedgehog, bird, lizard, mouse
The people use 6 different means of transport: snowmobile, skateboard, bike, van, subway, trike
1. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
2. the person driving the van is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
3. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
5. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
6. the person driving the van is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
7. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
8. the person driving the subway is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2    |      3      |     4     |     5     |    6    |
| Pet   | mouse | guinea-pig  | hedgehog    | bird  | hamster      | lizard    |
| Transport      | skateboard  | trike | subway | snowmobile | van | bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-2::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: tea, sprite, milk, hot-chocolate, juice, 7up
City: rome, miami, liverpool, berlin, colone, london
1. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
2. the person traveling to london is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
3. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person traveling to london##1
4. the person traveling to liverpool is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1
6. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
7. the person drinking 7up is the person traveling to london##1
8. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
9. the person drinking tea is the person traveling to liverpool##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3     |   4    |     5      |   6    |
| Beverage   | tea   | juice | sprite | 7up | hot-chocolate     | milk  |
| City           | liverpool | miami    | rome      | london  | berlin | colone |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-3::.
6 different games are played: poker, scrabble, whist, bridge, canasta, monopoly
There are 6 different favourite colors: amber, white, coral, blue, orange, chestnut
1. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
2. the person who likes blue is on the right of the person playing poker##1
3. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
4. the person playing whist is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
5. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
6. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person who likes white##1
7. the person who likes blue is on the far right##1
8. the person who likes coral is the person playing bridge##1
9. the person playing whist is the person who likes blue##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4     |   5    |     6     |
| Game   | bridge   | monopoly   | canasta      | scrabble | poker  | whist   |
| Color   | coral | chestnut | amber | white   | orange | blue |

