.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-4::.
There are 6 different nationalities: pakistani, indonesian, nigerian, dutch, colombian, turkish
6 different games are played: whist, scrabble, poker, bridge, mah-jongg, go
1. the person playing whist is on the far left##1
2. the nigerian is on the far left##1
3. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person playing go##1
4. the turkish is on the left of the colombian##1
5. the person playing go is the dutch##1
6. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
7. the colombian is on the far right##1
8. the person playing poker is on the right of the pakistani##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |     3      |     4      |   5   |    6    |
| Nationality   | nigerian  | dutch | pakistani      | indonesian  | turkish | colombian |
| Game     | whist | go  | mah-jongg | poker | bridge  | scrabble    |

