.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-5::.
6 different pets are kept: rabbit, lizard, turtle, goldfish, pony, fish
There are 6 different favourite colors: turquise, blood-red, black, pink, lavender, ebony
 1. the person who likes black is the owner of the rabbit##1
 2. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1
 3. the person who likes lavender is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
 4. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the person who likes turquise##1
 5. the person who likes turquise is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
 6. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the person who likes black##1
 7. the owner of the fish is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
 8. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person who likes turquise##1
 9. the person who likes black is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
10. the owner of the goldfish is the person who likes ebony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4     |     5      |    6    |
| Pet         | goldfish | fish | rabbit | pony | lizard | turtle  |
| Color   | ebony  | pink  | black  | turquise | lavender      | blood-red |

