.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-6::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: fanta, soy-milk, coffee, cola, 7up, tea
The people use 6 different means of transport: tram, subway, van, helicopter, taxi, motorbike
1. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
2. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
3. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
4. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
5. the person driving the taxi is the person drinking tea##1
6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person driving the van##1
7. the person driving the tram is on the far right##1
8. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
9. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |    5    |    6     |
| Beverage   | tea    | coffee    | fanta | 7up     | soy-milk   | cola     |
| Transport   | taxi | subway | motorbike | van | helicopter | tram |

