.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-7::.
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: sailing, golf, surfing, handball, rowing, soccer
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: lily, begonia, rose, iris, tulip, daisy
1. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
2. the person who growstulip is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
3. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person who growslily##1
4. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
5. the person who's sport is handball is the person who growsdaisy##1
6. the person who's sport is surfing is the person who growsrose##1
7. the person who growslily is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
8. the person who's sport is golf is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |   3   |     4      |   5   |     6      |
| Sport         | golf       | soccer     | handball | surfing | rowing | sailing |
| Flower   | begonia | tulip | daisy | rose     | lily  | iris       |

