.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-8::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: photography, camping, dancing, card-games, singing, baking
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: february, august, september, june, april, march
1. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person who's birthday is in april##1
2. the person who's birthday is in march is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
3. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
4. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
5. the person who's birthday is in august is the person who's hobby is baking##1
6. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
7. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
8. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2     |     3      |     4      |   5   |       6       |
| Hobby   | baking | photography  | singing     | dancing    | camping  | card-games          |
| Birthday         | august  | february | september | april | june | march |

