.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-9::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  entrepreneur, paramedic, musician, doctor, security-guard, dancer
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: volleyball, soccer, lacrosse, golf, basketball, water-polo
1. the doctor is on the left of the dancer##1
2. the musician is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
3. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
4. the person who's sport is water-polo is the entrepreneur##1
5. the doctor is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
6. the dancer is on the left of the entrepreneur##1
7. the entrepreneur is on the right of the dancer##1
8. the security-guard is on the left of the paramedic##1
9. the entrepreneur is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2     |    3     |   4    |       5       |     6      |
| Job    | security-guard | paramedic | doctor | dancer    | entrepreneur | musician      |
| Sport   | lacrosse   | volleyball     | soccer      | basketball | water-polo           | golf |

