2. the person drinking water is on the far right##1
3. the person traveling to hannover is the person drinking iced-tea##1
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
5. the person traveling to venice is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left##1
7. the person drinking juice is the person traveling to miami##1
8. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
9. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |   3    |    4    |   5    |    6     |
| Beverage          | iced-tea | juice   | milk  | fanta    | hot-chocolate  | water |
| City   | hannover   | miami | prague | paris | san-francisco | venice |

