The people have 6 different hobbies: fishing, video-games, collecting, card-games, photography, skydiving
6 different pets are kept: ferret, goldfish, bird, goat, chinchilla, rat
1. the owner of the goldfish is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
3. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
4. the owner of the goat is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
5. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
7. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
8. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
9. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3     |   4   |    5    |    6    |
| Hobby   | photography | skydiving | card-games    | video-games | collecting  | fishing |
| Pet     | goldfish    | chinchilla | goat | rat   | bird | ferret    |

