.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-15::.
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: july, october, january, november, february, march
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: musical, animation, fantasy, superhero, zombie, spy
1. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
2. the person watching spy movies is on the far right##1
3. the person who's birthday is in january is the person watching superhero movies##1
4. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
5. the person who's birthday is in november is the person watching animation movies##1
6. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
7. the person watching fantasy movies is the person who's birthday is in march##1
8. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
9. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |   2   |    3     |     4      |     5     |     6      |
| Birthday        | january     | february | october   | november      | march | july |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | zombie  | musical | animation | fantasy   | spy     |

