.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-20::.
City: colone, hannover, prague, miami, berlin, paris
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, oliveros, dunhill, old-henry, bluemaster, siglo
1. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1
2. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
3. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
4. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1
5. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
6. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1
7. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1
8. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1
9. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |     2     |     3      |   4    |   5   |     6      |
| City   | hannover | paris     | berlin       | prague  | miami | colone    |
| Cigar     | siglo  | swisher | oliveros | old-henry | bluemaster  | dunhill |

 